unittitle_ssm: Military Order of the Loyal Legion of the United States, New York Commandery Records
abstract_ssm: The records of the Military Order of the Loyal Legion of the United States consists primarily of routine correspondence to and from officers of the Legion. There are also a few interesting papers and artifacts from the Civil War.
